The archive should contain the following:

   AppTrashcan (dir)
      C (dir )
         EmptyTrash
         Trash
      AppTrashcan
      AppTrashcan.Guide
      AppTrashcan.Guide.info
      AppTrashcan
      Install
      Install.info
