@node Installation "Installation"
@next Usage
@prev Distribution
Just double click on the Install icon.

The installation uses the Commodore© Installer utility. This will install
the program and this AmigaGuide© file to where you want.

The Commodore© Installer utility is not included in the archive, but you
should either find it on the Workbench Hard Drive Install Disk, or on a
Fred Fish disk.
@endnode

